# Database Migrations

This directory contains Alembic database migrations for the Issue Tracker API.

## Commands

### Create a new migration
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "Description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

### Revert last migration
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

### Show current migration version
```bash
alembic current
```

### Show migration history
```bash
alembic history
```

## Initial Migration

The initial migration (`001_initial_schema`) creates all the base tables:
- users
- projects
- issues
- labels
- comments
- project_members (association table)
- assignments (association table)
- issue_labels (association table)
